{"slug":"sirkuler-23-522e-10953","reference":"Sirkuler_23_522E","gazette":"Official Gazette dated 01 June 2023 and numbered 32208","title":"Anti-dumping duty introduced for fabrics originating in/consigned from the Republic of North Macedonia and Bosnia and Herzegovina","date":"12 Haziran 2023","bodyHtml":"<p>The investigation regarding the circumvention of the measures initiated by the Ministry of Trade Import General Directorate against imports of \"synthetic textile fabrics made from synthetic filament yarn (for clothing)\" classified under customs tariff position 54.07 originating from North Macedonia and Bosnia-Herzegovina, and \"textile fabrics made from synthetic or artificial staple fibers\" classified under customs tariff positions 55.13, 55.14, 55.15, and 55.16 originating from North Macedonia, has been completed.</p><p>As a result of the investigation, anti-dumping duties ranging from 21percent to 44 percent of the CIF value will be imposed on the import of fabrics classified under customs tariff positions 54.07, 55.13, 55.14, 55.15, and 55.16 originating from the relevant countries. The anti-dumping duties is applicable starting from 01.06.2023.</p><p><a  href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2023/06/20230601-9.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Click here for the Communiqué on the Prevention of Unfair\r\nCompetition in Imports (No: 2023/20).</b></a><o></o></p><p xss=removed>Anti-dumping table for heading 54.07;<o></o></p><div align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"548\" xss=removed>\r\n <tbody><tr xss=removed>\r\n  <td width=\"143\" nowrap=\"\" xss=removed>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" xss=removed><b><span xss=removed>Country of Origin/Origin<u1></u1></span></b><span xss=removed><o></o></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"175\" nowrap=\"\" xss=removed>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" xss=removed><b><span xss=removed>Company Name<u1></u1></span></b>